86684,"uid":16123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cad.gov.hk/chinese/for_travellers.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cad.gov.hk%2Fchinese%2Ffor_travellers.html&d=c2wSda5U6HdSVseeXWl8GAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c144ee9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cad.gov.hk/chinese/for_travellers.html</a><br />\n<br />\n以下是一些乘客可攜帶上飛機之危險品例子及其相關限制：<br />\n<br />\n*化妝用品包括噴霧罐﹝如噴髮膠、香水、古龍水﹞，總容量不得多於2公升，而每件物品的淨容量不多於0.5公升<br />\n<br />\nHand carry應該可以帶，但要拿袋裝住同埋check個時拿出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cad.gov.hk/chinese/for_travellers.html#restrict\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cad.gov.hk%2Fchinese%2Ffor_travellers.html%23restrict&d=c2wSda5U6HdSVseeXWl8GAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0af09fee\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cad.gov.hk/chinese/for_travellers.html#restrict</a>"},{"pid":"01f72c50844c06aa4aa0eb4adb2b29584c7dc537","tid":286684,"uid":15103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.cad.gov.hk/chinese/for_travellers.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cad.gov.hk%2Fchinese%2Ffor_travellers.html&d=c2wSda5U6HdSVseeXWl8GAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c144ee9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cad.gov.hk/chinese/for_travellers.html</a><br />\n<br />\n以下是一些乘客可攜帶上飛機之危險品例子及其相關限制：<br />\n<br />\n*化妝用品包括噴霧罐﹝如噴髮膠、香水、古龍水﹞，總容量不得多於2公升，而每件物品的淨容量不多於0.5公升<br />\n<br />\nHand carry應該可以帶，但要拿袋裝住同埋check個時拿出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cad.gov.hk/chinese/for_travellers.html#restrict\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cad.gov.hk%2Fchinese%2Ffor_travellers.html%23restrict&d=c2wSda5U6HdSVseeXWl8GAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0af09fee\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cad.gov.hk/chinese/for_travellers.html#restrict</a></blockquote><br />\n但返嚟既話係咪都係跟呢個規矩???"},{"pid":"fb5d3b2daf9a7392c7c59b8f1c8f25c72fede31a","tid":286684,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"每支唔過100ml,入曬落透明膠袋度，拎出黎分開過xray"},{"pid":"1047dfc8ecfd474e4f4d5aee51509eb5b86af330","tid":286684,"uid":15103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T20:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每支唔過100ml,入曬落透明膠袋度，拎出黎分開過xray</blockquote><br />\n止汗劑例外??"},{"pid":"15ef7b032339a5f19824b682074e38d6335f59e8","tid":286684,"uid":367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T22:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每支唔過100ml,入曬落透明膠袋度，拎出黎分開過xray</blockquote><br />\n止汗劑例外??</blockquote><br />\n點解可以例外？<br />\n屌去到當地先買得啦"}]}